title: Second Harvest Locations, Toronto 2009
name: Second Harvest Locations, Toronto 2009
description:
This is a shapefile of second harvest food banks in Toronto from toronto.ca/open. Uploaded into Geocommons as shp, dbf, and shx files. 

Agencies that provide meals, food, nutritious breakfasts for a variety of clients. Agencies included are Daily Bread, Foodshare, Meals on Wheels, North York Harvest, Salvation Army, Second Harvest.
